# Room Name - TryHackMe: Missing Person
Date: 16 March 2026
Difficulty: Easy
Category: OSINT

# Scenario
Use your OSINT skills to help the police track down a missing person. The challenge provided task files containing images, and required correlating real-world data across multiple open-source intelligence sources to piece together the missing person's location and contact information.

# Tools Used
- Browser (web search & research)
- AI Assistant (image analysis / time estimation)
- Instagram
- Facebook
- Photos / Image metadata analysis

# What I Did
- Downloaded the task files, a ZIP archive containing two .jpg images: one of food and one of a MotoGP event.
- Examined the MotoGP image and identified the circuit name visible in the photo. Searched online to find its commercial name: Pertamina Mandalika International Street Circuit, Lombok, Indonesia.
- Searched for the MotoGP event schedule at that circuit and identified the event dates: 03-05 October 2025.
- Examined the food image and identified the restaurant name visible on the table/decor: Cantina Mexicana.
- Used AI to estimate the time of day the photo was taken based on lighting and visual cues.
- Searched for bars near Kuta, Lombok (the area closest to Mandalika Circuit) and cross-referenced addresses against the expected answer format to identify the correct bar: Jl. Raya Kuta, Kuta, Kec. Pujut, Kabupaten Lombok Tengah, Nusa Tenggara Barat
- Searched for after-party events held at the bar around the MotoGP event dates. Found an Instagram video from the after-party which revealed the DJ's name: Bong Leleh.
- Searched for famous caves near Lombok and matched results against the expected answer pattern: Gua Sumur
- Looked up DJ Bong Leleh's social media accounts and found a Facebook page for Gua Sumur that tagged the DJ's account, which contained the phone number: 85333137345

# What I Found
- Circuit: Pertamina Mandalika International Street Circuit
- Event Dates: 03-05 October 2025
- Restaurant: Cantina Mexicana
- Bar Address: Jl. Raya Kuta, Kuta, Kec. Pujut, Kabupaten Lombok Tengah, Nusa Tenggara Barat
- DJ Name: Bong Leleh
- Cave: Gua Sumur
